<h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
Page Not Found
</h1>

<p class="text-slate-600 text-lg mb-10">
The page you're looking for doesn't exist or may have moved.
Let's get you back on track.
</p>

<a href="index.html"
class="inline-block bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl font-bold transition">
Calculate My Solar Savings
</a>

<div class="mt-12 pt-10 border-t border-slate-100">

<h2 class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 mb-6">
Popular Pages
</h2>

<div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">

<a href="solar-subsidy-india.html" class="px-4 py-2 bg-slate-100 rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-200 transition">
